race.description: Met Apartments Port Lincoln Maiden Plate
race.comment: STARS ARE ALIGNING (12) went close to making the perfect return here two weeks ago, nabbed late after leading them up. Sure to have tightened with that run and has the speed to offset the draw. Ready to shed the tag. MAKENZIE (9) resumes and looks to have come on nicely during the break, with solid work in readiness. Draws to get all the favours for Milnes and is expected to play a major role. JURA VAUDOIS (8) hasn't been as effective in her last two after kicking off the prep with close finishes, but gets in well with the claim and is a big chance to rebound. DRAGON FISH (6) improved sharply here last time when chasing gamely into the placings. Open to further improvement third-up, though likely to drift back from the wide draw. Watch for her charging late.
